Interface ObjectTimeFinder.TimeFinderListener<O,I>

  • Type Parameters:

    public static interface ObjectTimeFinder.TimeFinderListener<O,I>
    An interface for objects that wish to be informed of object tracking events during the time finder's execution.

    David Dupplaw (dpd@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
